}}'''為生命遊行'''（March for Life）是一年一度在美國首都[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華盛頓]]舉行的集会和游行。該遊行的舉辦時間基本上是[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]在1973年[[羅訴韋德案|羅訴韋德案]]一案中作出的堕胎合法化的裁决周年纪念日當天或前后举行。該游行的目的是抗议和反對[[堕胎|堕胎]]並要求推翻[[羅訴韋德案|羅訴韋德案]]的判決。該遊行是由生命教育和辩护基金（March for Life Education and Defense Fund）負責组织<ref>{{Cite web|title=About the March for Life|url=http://marchforlife.org/about-us/|accessdate=September 8, 2018|work=marchforlife.org|archive-date=2019-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930134611/https://marchforlife.org/about-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|author=Morrow|first=Brendan|title=Young anti-abortion marchers look forward to 'post-Roe America'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jan/23/young-anti-abortion-marchers-washington-march-for-life|accessdate=January 24, 2020|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|date=January 23, 2020|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203041545/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jan/23/young-anti-abortion-marchers-washington-march-for-life|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

